                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                  <locus from="2ra" to="71rb"/>
                  <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1931Mashaf">Maṣḥafa gǝnzat (general record)</title>

                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                      <locus from="5ra" to="6ra"/>
                      <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1931Mashaf#Priests">Reading for the funeral of the priests,
                        The Parables of the Talents (Mt 25, 14-30)
                     </title>
                      <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        <locus target="#5ra"/>
                      <hi rend="rubric">ወንጌል፡ ዘማቴዎስ፡ እስመ፡ ከመ፡ <sic resp="DN">ከመ</sic>፡ ብእሲ፡</hi> ዘይነግድ፡
                       ወጸውዓ፡ አግብርቲሁ፡ ወወሃቦሙ፡ ንዋየ፡ ይትገበር፨ ወቦ፡ ለዘወሀቦ፡ ፭፡ መክሊተ፡ ወቦ፡ ለዘወሀቦ፡ ፪፡ መክሊተ፡
                      </incipit>
                        <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                          <locus target="#6ra"/>
                        ብካይ፡ ወሐቄ፡ ስነን፨
                        </explicit>
                    </msItem>

                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                    <locus from="5ra" to="6vb"/>
                    <locus from="2ra" to="2vb"/>
                    <title type="complete">Mǝlṭān and ʾaryām-antiphons for the priests</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      <locus target="#5ra"/>
                    <hi rend="rubric">እሰግድ፡ ለከ፡ አብ፡ ቀዳማ</hi>ዊ፡ እሰግድ፡ ለከ፡ ወልድ፡ ዋህድ፡
                    ንሰግድለከ፡ ኦመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፨ ወሐሥሥ፡ በኃቤከ፡ በእንተ፡ ነፍስ፡ ገብርከ፡ እገለ፡ ዘወጽአ፡ እምዝንቱ፡ ሥጋ፡ ከመ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ አበዊነ፡
                    ለይኩን፡ ሎቱ፡ ዕረፍተ፡
                      </incipit>
                    <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                      <locus target="#2ra"/>
                      ከመ፡ ትባኢ፡ ሃገረ፡ እንተ፡ ኬንያሃ፡ ወሐዋጺሃ&gt; ወልደ፡ እግዚአብሔ<gap reason="lost"/>፨
                    </explicit>
                    <note>The text on <locus target="#6vb"/> ends with
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ፍቁራኒሁ፡ ለብ፡ ኄራን፡ መተንበላ</foreign>.
                  <locus target="#2"/> is in the reversed position, and the continuation is on the verso-side,
                  <locus target="#2va"/>, cp. <foreign xml:lang="gez">ን፡ ኅቡረ፡ ይባርክዎ፡ ለአብ፨</foreign>.</note>
                  </msItem>

                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                    <locus from="7ra" to="11rb"/>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1931Mashaf#FuneralProcession">Directives and readings for the first two stations
                      of the funeral procession</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    <locus target="#7ra"/><hi rend="rubric">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወል</hi>ድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ <gap reason="lost" unit="chars" extent="1"/><hi rend="rubric">
                    አምላክ፡ መጽሐ</hi>ፈ፡ ፍትሐት፡ ዘኵሎሙ፡ <hi rend="rubric">አበው፡ ምንባብ።</hi>
                      ወ<sic>ተብል፡</sic> አሌፍ፡ እስከ፡ ላሜድ፨ ወእምዝ፡ ትብል፡ ሶበ፡ ታወጽኦ፡ ለግኑዝ፡ እማኅደሩ፨ ወትበል፡ ሜም፡ እስከ፡ ሳምነት፨ ወታአርፍ፡ በፍ<hi rend="rubric">ኖት፡
                      ፩፡ ምዕራፍ፡ ወእምዝ፡ ትብል፡ ቅድመ፡ ወንጌል፡</hi> ዘ፶ወ፱፨ ወመጽአኒ፡ ድንጋፄ፡ ሞት፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ፍርሃት፡ ወረዓድ፡ አኃዘኒ፡ ወደፈነኒ፡ ጽልመት
                      </incipit>
                      <note>Ps 118 “from Alef to Lamed” should be read for the 1st station,
                       various other texts and Mk 12:18-28 (but the manuscript refers to Luke).
                       For the 2nd station, Lk 16:19-31 and the Second Prayer about the Deceased (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ ዳግማይ፡ በእንተ፡ እለ፡ ኖሙ፡</foreign>), other readings
                       and prayers. Ps 118 “from Qof to Taw” for entering the church, “greeting of the <foreign xml:lang="gez">tābot</foreign>”.</note>
                    </msItem>

                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                    <locus from="11rb" to="14vb"/>
                    <locus from="4ra" to="4vb"/>
                    <locus from="15ra" to="15rb"/>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1629Homily">Homily by Jacob of Serug</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    <locus target="#11rb"/><hi rend="rubric">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አ</hi>ምላክ፨ ድርሳን፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ወብፁዕ፡
                     አባ፡ ያዕቆብ፡ ዘስሩግ፡ ዘደረሰ፡ በእንተ፡ እለ፡ ኖሙ፡ ካህናት፡ ወዲያቆናት፡ እለ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፨ ሰምዑ፡ ኦፍቁራንየ፡ ከመ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ አምላከ፡
                     ሕያዋን፡ ወምዉታን፡ ውእቱ፨
                  </incipit>
                    <note>One folium missing between <locus target="#14"/> and <locus target="#15"/> is
                    <locus target="#4"/> which is in the reserved position,
                  cp. <foreign xml:lang="gez">በከመ፡ ተ</foreign> (<locus target="#14vb"/>) and
                  <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወከፍከ፡</foreign> (<locus target="#4va"/>)</note>
                    </msItem>


                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
                  <locus from="15rb" to="20vb"/>
                  <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1931Mashaf#Deacons">Readings and prayers over
                    the deceased deacons</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    <locus target="#15rb"/><hi rend="rubric">ግንዘት፡ ዲያቆናት፡</hi> ጳውሎስ፡ ቆረንቶስ፡ ወኵሉ፡ በበሥርዓቱ፡ ቀዳሜ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ውእቱ፡ ወእምዝ፡ እለ፡ በክርስቶስ፡
                      በምጽአቱ፨ ወማኅለቅቱሰ፡ አመ፡ ተወፈየ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወአመ፡ ተሥዕረ፡ ኵሉ፡ መኮንን፡ ወኵሉ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ወኵሉ፡ ኃይል፨ እስመ፡ ሀለዎ፡ ይነግሥ፡ እስከ፡ አመ፡
                      ይገብኡ፡ ኵሉ፡ ጸላእቱ፡ ታሕተ፡ እግሪሁ፨
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>

                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6">
                    <locus from="20vb" to="22va"/>
                  <title type="complete" corresp="LIT1931Mashaf#Matthew">Prayer of Matthew the Apostle</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      <locus target="#20vb"/>
                    <hi rend="rubric">ጸሎተ፡ ማ<gap reason="lost" unit="chars" quantity="1"/>ዎስ፡ ሐዋርያ፡</hi> እባርከከ፡ እግዚእየ፡
                    በኵሉ፡ ጊዜ፡ ዘኢይበሊ፡ ማኅደሩ፡ ልዑል፡ ዘይነብር፡ ላዕለ፡ ኵሉ፡ መልዕልት፡ እሰብሐከ፡ ዘኢኀብአ፡ ርእሶ፡
                    </incipit>
                    </msItem>

                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7">
                    <locus from="22va" to="22vb"/>
                    <locus from="3ra" to="3rb"/>
                    <title type="incomplete">Absolution and prayers</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      <locus target="#22va"/><hi rend="rubric">አብስልዋጥስ</hi><add resp="DN">፡</add> ትብል፡ በዜማ፡ ግንዘት፤
                    ኦእግዚኦ፡ መፍቀሪ፡ ሰብእ፡ ኄር፡ እግዚእየ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ እስእለከ፡ ኢትግድፈኒ፡ በጸጋምከ፡ ምስለ፡ ጉባኤ፡ ኃጥአን፡
                      </incipit>

                      <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        <locus target="#3rb"/>
                        ይስእል፡ በእንተአነ፡ በጸጋ፡ ወምሕረት፡ ለዓለመ፨
                      </explicit>
                  <note>The first part of the text ends on <locus target="#22vb"/> with <foreign xml:lang="gez">መሐሪ፡ ውእቱ፡ ይሠ</foreign>).
                  The continuation is on <locus target="#3ra"/>, cp. <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሃል፡ ሕዝቦ፡
                  እስመ፡ ኄር፡ ውእቱ፡ ወመፍቃሬ፡ ሰብእ፡</foreign>.</note>
                  </msItem>


                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.8">
                      <locus from="3ra" to="3vb"/>
                      <locus from="23ra" to="24rb"/>
                      <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1931Mashaf">Story of release of an impure rich man from
                      the Hell</title>
                      <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        <locus target="#3ra"/>
                        ወሀሎ፡ ፩፡ ብእሲ፡ ባዕል፡ በአሐቲ፡ ሀገር፡ ዘኢይፈርሆ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡
                      </incipit>
                      <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        <locus target="#24rb"/>
                        ወኩሎሙ፡ ማኅበረ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ ወሰማዕት፡ ይእዜኒ፡ ወዘልፈኒ፡ ወለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፨
                      </explicit>

                      <note>The text on the misplaced <locus target="#3vb"/> ends
                      with <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወዕሙቅ፡ ጥቀ፡ ወም</foreign>,
                      and the continuation is <locus target="#23ra"/>, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሉእ፡ ጽልመተ፡ ዘተከረየ፡ በእሳት፡ ወተይ፨
                      ወየዓርግ፡ እምውስቴቱ፡ ጢስ፡</foreign>.</note>
                    </msItem>


               <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.9">
                      <locus from="24rb" to="26vb"/>
                      <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1931Mashaf#Exhortations">Exhortation to the breathen to celebrate the commemoration feasts</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                          <locus target="#24rb"/>
                          <hi rend="rubric">መፍትው፡ ለነ፡</hi> ኦአኃውየ፡ <pb n="24va"/>ንግበር፡ ተዝካሮሙ፡ ለምዉታን፡ በማዕጠንት፡ ወዕጣን፡ ወቍርባን፨ እስመ፡ ይበቍዖሙ፡
                        ወይከውን፡ ዕረፍተ፡ ለነፍሶሙ፡ በከመ፡ ትቤሎ፡ እግዚእትነ፡ <hi rend="rubric">ማርያም፡</hi> ለብፁዕ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡
                         ሊቀ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ ሶበ፡ ተሥዕለ፡ እንዘ፡ ይብል፡ መሥዋእተ፡ ወቊርባነ፡
                       </incipit>
                    </msItem>

                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.10">
                      <locus from="26vb" to="29rb"/>
                      <title type="complete">Supplications <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2605Zayena">Za-yǝnaggǝś</ref> for all the dead
                      and other prayers</title>
                      <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        <locus target="#26vb"/>ወካዕበ፡ ናስተበቍዖ፡ ለእግዚአ፡ ኵሉ፡ አምላክነ፡ አኃዜ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዘይነግሥ፡ ለኵሉ፡ ዓለም፡ አቡሁ፡
                        ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፤ አምላክ፡ ዘመናፍስት፡ ወለኵሉ፡ ዘሥጋ፡
                      በእንተ፡ እለ፡ ኖሙ፡ አኃዊነ፡ ናስተበቍዕ፡ ከመ፡ ታዕርፍ፡ ነፍሶሙ፡ ውስተ፡ መካን፡ ሥዑር፡ ኀበ፡ ማየ፡ ዕረፍት፡</incipit>
                    </msItem>


                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.11">
                      <locus from="29rb" to="32rb"/>
                      <title type="complete">Absolution prayer</title>
                      <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        <locus target="#29rb"/><hi rend="rubric"><sic resp="DN">እዚእ፡</sic> እግዚኦ፡
